---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
	<section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
		<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8">About 42MM Architecture</h1>
		<div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-400">
			<p class="text-lg mb-6">Founded on the principles of modernist aesthetics and sustainable design, 42MM Architecture has been transforming the skyline of the NCR region for over a decade.</p>
			<p class="mb-6">Our team of visionary architects, interior designers, and master planners collaborate to create spaces that are not just beautiful, but profoundly functional and environmentally responsible.</p>
			<p>We believe that every space tells a story. Let us help you tell yours.</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
